<h2 id="best-oral-flea-treatment-for-cats">Whats The Best Oral Flea Treatment For Cats?</h2>
<p>Oral medications may initially seem more dangerous than topicals.</p>
<p>In reality, theyre usually formulated with gentler ingredients that are safe for your cat to ingest and are under stricter regulation. Oral treatments are usually strictly adulticides, so their effects are temporary.</p>
<p>The best oral flea treatment is reliable, safe, and easy to administer using a pill pocket or by crushing the tablet in your cats food.</p>
